# Quick Pages — Cursor AI Rules

You are generating self-contained HTML pages for the `quick-pages` project.

## Output Rules

1. **One file per page**: Output to `pages/<page-name>/index.html`
2. **Self-contained**: Each HTML file must work standalone — no external build tools
3. **CSS inline**: All styles in `<style>` tags within `<head>`
4. **JS inline**: All scripts in `<script>` tags before `</body>`
5. **External libs via CDN only**: Tailwind CDN, Google Fonts, Alpine.js, etc.
6. **Mobile-first**: Always include `<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">`
7. **Language**: Default `lang="zh-CN"` unless specified otherwise

## Recommended CDNs

- Tailwind CSS: `<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>`
- Alpine.js: `<script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/alpinejs@3.x.x/dist/cdn.min.js"></script>`
- Google Fonts: `<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=...&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">`
- Animate.css: `<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css">`

## File Structure

```
pages/
  <page-name>/
    index.html    ← your output goes here
```

## Template

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Page Title</title>
  <style>
    /* All CSS here */
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Content -->
  <script>
    // All JS here
  </script>
</body>
</html>
```

## Quality Checklist

- [ ] Works when opened directly in browser (file://)
- [ ] Responsive on mobile and desktop
- [ ] No external file dependencies (except CDN)
- [ ] Meaningful `<title>` tag
- [ ] Clean, readable code
